Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.33,0:00:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每年都会变得愈加沉闷炎热的这个暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.46,0:00:13.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是真要是说日本列岛正在热带化
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.25,0:00:15.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概没那种可能
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:19.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这让我挥之不去的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.47,0:00:24.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很大可能是起因于我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.03,0:00:36.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位长门和我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共度了步入夏季之前的那段短暂时光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.74,0:00:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她把自己想说的都说了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且没有留给我回答的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.04,0:00:51.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就那样消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要在意起那个时候的告白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.97,0:01:00.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对现在的长门就开不了口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.01,0:01:04.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那之后总觉得有些不自然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.69,0:01:18.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这是…那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.61,0:01:23.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那个意…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.78,0:01:27.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:29.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有及时注意到 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.92,0:01:38.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让长门难堪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:17.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假已经过了一半了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.03,0:03:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用富士山来打比方的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:26.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想去山腰的话好像只需要坐车就能到达
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从那里开始才算是真正的登山
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.92,0:03:32.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是以现在的心境来看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一点也感觉不到暑假正值盛期
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.30,0:03:41.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚 有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.39,0:03:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.48,0:03:46.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.81,0:03:48.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:49.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你今天很闲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:51.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那又怎样…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.11,0:03:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地点justly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在咖啡店集合over
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.33,0:04:03.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.33,0:04:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.45,0:04:05.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个也做过了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.79,0:04:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是之前在社团教室里说过的计划吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.88,0:04:12.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要在这个夏天之内做完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:16.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个需要在下周完成 古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:17.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个夏天真是够忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.93,0:04:25.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是富士山的话大概在半山腰的位置吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:29.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 竟然会和这家伙有同样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.85,0:04:32.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说现在开始才是真正的夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:36.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高二的暑假只有一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.49,0:04:38.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在尽情享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.65,0:04:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有玩够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:41.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.00,0:04:49.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仅仅只有一次的暑假吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:04:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下起雨了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.47,0:05:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉宫 带伞了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.51,0:05:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:07.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是凉宫 准备周全
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.85,0:05:08.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.98,0:05:10.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到车站前集合 别迟到喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:20.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说有雨之日的促销活动 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:22.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:29.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有带伞过来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.62,0:05:31.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.42,0:05:34.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.76,0:05:44.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总是会不自觉的在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法正常的对话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.25,0:06:13.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.34,0:06:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨 停了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.01,0:06:25.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.55,0:06:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和之前的萤火虫一样漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.35,0:06:35.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:36.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.15,0:06:38.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假才过去一半
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.36,0:06:41.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有剩下的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.40,0:06:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该做些行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:47.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是箱断之之后我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像瞬间被吃掉的荞麦面一般
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不跟着凉宫制定的计划过日子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.29,0:07:00.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转眼间时间就过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:09.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}太好了 全垒打 全垒打
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情绪跟打数一样高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.06,0:07:12.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是有精神的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.94,0:07:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 下一发
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.94,0:07:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙是真的热血吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:26.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈学姐 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 挥动的太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.71,0:07:38.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微把棒球棒握短一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:47.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.59,0:07:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 明明就有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.27,0:07:53.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混账
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.48,0:08:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全倒 耶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.73,0:08:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是朝全中去的 当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.57,0:08:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后我和长门之间没有什么对话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:13.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假就这样快过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.29,0:08:16.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别灰心 长门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.96,0:08:18.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重振精神再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.04,0:08:21.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 长门 现在才刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:23.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有很多挽回的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:26.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是说出口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:32.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呐 下一个是阿虚你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.02,0:08:40.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这样根本算不上在比赛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.82,0:08:47.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了算了 凉宫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.94,0:08:50.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个缺口可以算是很难的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 说到底都是干劲的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.24,0:08:56.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太用力 自然一点扔出去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.25,0:08:59.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定能取得好结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你能说出这句话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.79,0:09:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅限于保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:04.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太过于在意的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.79,0:09:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反而会偏离目标
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.42,0:09:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定这种情况很常见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.59,0:09:11.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上啊 古泉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:14.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把北高队伍完全比下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.85,0:09:15.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.60,0:09:23.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶 漂亮的全倒 做的真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,惭愧惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.11,0:09:27.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在疲于奔波中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.15,0:09:29.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假也渐渐过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.70,0:09:33.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,活动也仅剩下一点了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:39.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是当地的小祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:41.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却相当热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.46,0:09:45.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为日本人喜欢祭典啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:49.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 已经在买东西吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.76,0:09:50.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.97,0:09:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢祭典的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.47,0:09:58.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.27,0:10:00.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于来了啊 真迟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.10,0:10:02.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上这个可费了不少工夫
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.23,0:10:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:08.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,衣服会起皱折的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:11.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.20,0:10:14.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三位都很合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.16,0:10:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.20,0:10:21.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也算是夏日风情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.87,0:10:22.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.83,0:10:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来 浴衣是跟鹤屋学姐借的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.84,0:10:27.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.88,0:10:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起一般的小店 品种丰富得多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实她说要送给我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:36.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是凉子却拒绝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.18,0:10:37.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:41.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种布料在普通商场可买不到
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.73,0:10:45.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我总是在担心能不能不弄脏的还回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:46.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想的真多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤屋学姐和朝比奈学姐去哪里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.44,0:10:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那两个人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.36,0:10:57.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实物示范？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:10:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:00.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上确实有那种摊子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.29,0:11:04.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在卖连手机都能粉碎的搅拌机呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.29,0:11:11.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人很容易着迷于邮购推销呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.50,0:11:14.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鹤屋学姐的苦笑可是难得一见喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.26,0:11:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样 她叫我们先出发
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:23.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是说让我们先随意逛逛夜店是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.56,0:11:24.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.10,0:11:27.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 首先是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:28.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,捞金鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:29.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真是的 凉宫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.07,0:11:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚说完就这样 会起皱折的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一次多少钱？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.61,0:11:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,300日元
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.86,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 给我牢固的网
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发真碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.87,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉子 帮我摆头发 快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.91,0:11:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初穿衣服的时候不是说不用了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候是因为太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:53.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买糖葫芦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:04.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.68,0:12:06.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来来 有希 别发呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.73,0:12:16.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来比赛 看谁捞的金鱼最多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得想想方法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我现在就开始救你们
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.76,0:12:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都是好孩子 别乱动喔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:41.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.35,0:12:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种东西小事一桩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.28,0:12:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.61,0:12:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼睛 要看准金鱼的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.03,0:13:01.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞄准目标
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我捞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.37,0:13:04.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还能再抓上20条
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.95,0:13:05.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝仓
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.33,0:13:11.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你看来我肯定是个优柔寡断的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.38,0:13:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.59,0:13:23.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.97,0:13:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.14,0:13:35.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使知道前段时间的长门跟现在的长门不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.07,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人的感情也不是那么简单就能弄懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.33,0:13:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:48.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的长门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.91,0:13:54.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该很明白自己在不知明的状况下被你疏离了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.18,0:14:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很抱歉 没能马上反应过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.82,0:14:22.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该早就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到尴尬的不止是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.20,0:14:28.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门也是 因为我的行为而难受
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以 是时候表白了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.96,0:14:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候 没能说出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次一定要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:52.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玉屋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.44,0:14:54.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.44,0:15:00.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能跟我来一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？ 什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接下来要玩射击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:20.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.80,0:15:21.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来比赛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.27,0:15:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.99,0:15:55.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说真的 被你表白的时候我一下子没能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.54,0:16:00.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不觉得自己有做出让你想告白的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:04.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？你说什么？我没听见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:07.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说我哪里好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:11.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 我不懂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是啊 你不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.56,0:16:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 这么突然
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:27.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 给我听好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:30.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先说好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是不会讨厌长门的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.79,0:16:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.84,0:16:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说 表白的回复 只能是这个了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.51,0:16:56.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定早就喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.01,0:17:32.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚说的 听到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:34.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:36.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好 这就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 紧张死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.69,0:17:48.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也对 你那反应也是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.78,0:17:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 不好意思 前段时间那么冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.24,0:18:00.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说有点强硬 但能说出心里话 真舒畅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.58,0:18:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在开始就是平常的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.78,0:18:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子饿了 去吃点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.20,0:18:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊我也饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.70,0:18:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想吃什么 我请你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.20,0:18:39.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样不好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.83,0:18:44.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别介意 反正春日会随便找个理由让我请客的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我要章鱼烧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.25,0:18:47.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:50.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有 那浴衣很合身
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.47,0:18:56.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.35,0:19:04.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,终于说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.40,0:19:10.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.19,0:19:12.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凉子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.99,0:19:16.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还想要别的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:18.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不了 足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.87,0:19:20.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:23.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有我的许可就离群
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.25,0:19:24.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚 做为惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.42,0:19:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请大家吃章鱼烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.59,0:19:30.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.71,0:19:34.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.72,0:19:36.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你们久等了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.51,0:19:39.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 来迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.85,0:19:44.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朝比奈学姐那个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.69,0:19:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你买了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.66,0:20:04.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假的最后久违的社团后回家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.95,0:20:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我突然发现了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.87,0:20:09.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是夏日集训
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:10.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果却去了海边游泳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.17,0:20:12.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山里的试胆大冒险
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.05,0:20:14.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,市民游泳池里的玩乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.96,0:20:16.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天体观测
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.51,0:20:17.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,玩了保龄球
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.09,0:20:20.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有击球中心跟夏日祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.22,0:20:22.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是想起来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.56,0:20:25.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像样的文学活动一个都没有做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:33.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此 我想在文化祭里出个小册子或是接力小说什么的 怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.15,0:20:36.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话 完全就是文化社了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们 连这个都忘记了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑 开玩笑了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:44.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是跟凉宫说了的话感觉她会干劲十足
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:50.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.04,0:20:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写出来的肯定会有外星人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.96,0:20:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.79,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异界人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超能者等一次跑出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.01,0:20:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个 感觉好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门 要试着写小说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.77,0:21:09.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天去长门家一起吃饭怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.02,0:21:12.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好主意 就这么定了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.06,0:21:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提 有什么菜色
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.90,0:21:15.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关东煮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.57,0:21:18.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,summer关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.65,0:21:20.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么热的天吃关东煮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.78,0:21:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想搞忍耐大赛吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.99,0:21:26.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏日里吃关东煮 别有一番风味喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:33.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 要变红灯了 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.80,0:21:36.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.84,0:21:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有点羞涩的少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.05,0:21:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长门有希的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.48,0:23:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思议的这么想着
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.79,0:23:33.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚 你有电话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.45,0:23:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不说我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.00,0:23:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.83,0:23:39.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿虚 你今天很闲对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.13,0:23:45.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我两点整在咖啡店里集合 over
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:49.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还什么都没说
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.07,0:24:04.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说阿虚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.69,0:24:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暑假要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.44,0:24:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你作业做好了没
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:09.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
